onNewDataDownloadFinished

void onNewDataDownloadFinished(int statusCode,
                               AntPlusGeocachePcc.GeocacheDeviceData downloadedData)
Receives the data from a DataDownloadFinished event.

Parameters:
statusCode - The AntPlusGeocachePcc.GeocacheRequestStatusCode defining the result of the download.
downloadedData - The complete set of data downloaded from the device or null if the download was unsuccessful. To see what data is present on the device iterate through the Bundle#keySet() comparing with the keys defined in AntPlusGeocachePcc.IpcDefines.GeocacheDataKeys.
